{"tid":1704460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 咩情況下 UN 會出 Peacekeeping Force?","createTime":"2019-11-10T16:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T17:00:15.000Z","uid":22713,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2559ef878d02dee1fb5fab47a4dad169bc3abbc5","tid":1704460,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"對UN 嘅工作好有興趣，係UN Peacekeeping Force website 見到維和部隊嘅工作包括<br />\n1. Protect civilians<br />\n2. Promote Human Rights<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://peacekeeping.un.org/en/what-we-do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeacekeeping.un.org%2Fen%2Fwhat-we-do&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=dcba2ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://peacekeeping.un.org/en/what-we-do</a> <br />\n假設一個police state ，而政府包庇縱容警察各種踐踏人權，甚至泯滅人性嘅行為，唔知符唔符合出維和部隊嘅criteria 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，見到UN Peacekeeping 有分 Military (好似比較適用於armed conflict 嘅情況) 同 UN Police，唔知有咩方法可以尋求聯合國出 Military 或者UN Police 保護人民呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMilitary: <a href=\"https://peacekeeping.un.org/en/military\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeacekeeping.un.org%2Fen%2Fmilitary&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=a8fdd2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://peacekeeping.un.org/en/military</a><br />\nUN Police: <a href=\"https://peacekeeping.un.org/en/un-police\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeacekeeping.un.org%2Fen%2Fun-police&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=f98cff3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://peacekeeping.un.org/en/un-police</a><br />\n<br />\n但係成個 deployment process 需時較長，所以想拋磚引玉，跪求高手指點可行性同埋點向聯合國申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：純學術討論"},{"pid":"e